      • create

        void create()
        Create any logically contained resources (relations, indices). There is no presumption that ILocatableResource.init() is suitable for invocation from create(). Instead, you are responsible for invoking ILocatableResource.init() from this method IFF it is appropriate to reuse its initialization logic.
